<article id="post-35825" class="post-35825 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-productivity category-profession tag-job-market tag-online-identity tag-web-presence tag-web-sites article legacy-format">
        <div class="blog__author">
            <time datetime="2011-09-08T15:00:23-04:00">September 8, 2011</time> by <a href="http://www.chronicle.com/blogs/profhacker/author/phacker" title="View all posts by Prof. Hacker" rel="author">Prof. Hacker</a>
